every day, so at the end of

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:22.960
day 1-- so at the beginning of a
certain billing cycle Jane's

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:25.050
credit card account had
a balance of $600.

00:01:25.050 --> 00:01:25.480
So we don't know.

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:26.910
She might have paid
