00:01:26.910 --> 00:01:28.170
So I'm not going to put
any labels here.

00:01:28.170 --> 00:01:30.350
But she starts at 600.

00:01:30.350 --> 00:01:36.580
And that's her balance until on
some day she pays off half

00:01:36.580 --> 00:01:40.190
