goes down like that.

00:01:40.190 --> 00:01:41.950
So the question is, what
is the average?

00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:46.680
So it's going to be $600 times a
certain number of days, plus

00:01:46.680 --> 00:01:50.270
$300 times a certain number
of days, divided by 30.

00:01:50.270 --> 00:01:51.190
So let me write that down.

00:01:51.190 --> 00:01:54.940
The average is going to be equal
to $600 times however

00:01:54.940 --> 00:01:59.610
many days she carried the $600
balance plus $300 times

00:01:59.610 --> 00:02:02.530
however many days she kept
the $300 balance.

00:02:02.530 --> 00:02:07.580
And that's going to
be 30 minus x.

00:02:07.580 --> 00:02:10.064
If she paid after 15 days, she
