00:02:14.730 --> 00:02:17.180
If she paid after one day, then
you would have the $300

00:02:17.180 --> 00:02:18.850
balance for 29 days.

00:02:18.850 --> 00:02:20.860
And all of that divided by 30.

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:22.170
That's the average.

00:02:22.170 --> 00:02:23.780
And I try to do that from the
get-go, because I just want to

00:02:23.780 --> 00:02:26.690
