00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:58.460
And I'm sure this time.

00:03:58.460 --> 00:04:00.750
Multiply both sides by
25, you get a number.

00:04:00.750 --> 00:04:02.450
And then you can distribute
this out.

00:04:02.450 --> 00:04:04.180
Add all the x terms.
Solve for x.

00:04:04.180 --> 00:04:07.190
And then once you solve for x,
you can just use this equation

00:04:07.190 --> 00:04:08.860
up here to figure out
the average daily

00:04:08.860 --> 00:04:11.460
balance for 30 days.

00:04:11.460 --> 00:04:14.680
So actually, each of these
statements independently are

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:16.630
sufficient to figure
out this problem.

00:04:16.630 --> 00:04:19.140
Actually, it was very critical
